<emphasis bold="true" box="[144,674,1355,1375]" pageId="35" pageNumber="409">
Figure 27. 
<taxonomicName authority="Biju &amp; Bossuyt, 2009" authorityName="Biju &amp; Bossuyt" authorityYear="2009" box="[273,582,1355,1374]" class="Amphibia" family="Rhacophoridae" genus="Philautus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Anura" pageId="35" pageNumber="409" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="chromasynchysi" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[273,582,1355,1374]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="409">Philautus chromasynchysi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[588,674,1356,1375]" pageId="35" pageNumber="409" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
A, holotype (BNHS 4433); B, paratype (BNHS 4438); C, paratype (BNHS 4442): all from Kurichiyarmala.
</paragraph>
